726492f-a.text:
Douglaston Parkway, west side, between 42nd and 43rd Avenues, showing the Douglaston Hose Company. The Parkway, here, was formerly named Main Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  April 12, 1927

726493f-a.text: Douglaston Parkway, west side, between Poplar Street(42nd Ave) and Willow Street(41st St), overlooking 235th Street(Main Ave/Alley Rd) showing Public School No. 98. Board of Education of the City of New York about 1931.
